Copy the URL for Windows Maps. For example, copy the URL https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/windows-maps/9wzdncrdtbvb. Note the series of letters at the end of the URL. For example, 9wzdncrdtbvb.
In a different tab, paste the following URL https://bspmts.mp.microsoft.com/v1/public/catalog/Retail/Products/<app id>/applockerdata, and then replace <app id>.

